text: Zsolt Lévai (born 3 August 1965) is a Hungarian rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Hungary Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Budapest
